notes: Rain disrupted play in England's innings for 43 minutes when they were 62/0 after 12.0 overs. The target was revised to 226 in 41 overs.

milestones.description: Wessels and Andrew Hudson's 151-run partnership is SA's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 74 between Wessels and Andrew Hudson
Allan Donald has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (10) for SA, going past Adrian Kuiper
Wessels and Andrew Hudson's 151-run partnership is SA's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 112 between Peter Kirsten and Wessels
